      *****************************************************************
       200-GMNSENI                               SECTION.
      *
           EVALUATE    MCP-EVENT                 ALSO    MCP-WIDGET
      *        戻る
               WHEN    "CLICKED"                 ALSO    "B01"
                   MOVE    SPACE                 TO  SPA-I0ID2-FLG
                   PERFORM 210-BACK
      *     登録
               WHEN    "CLICKED"                 ALSO    "B12"
                   MOVE    "OK"                  TO  SPA-I0ID2-FLG
                   PERFORM 210-BACK
           END-EVALUATE.
      *
       200-GMNSENI-EXT.
           EXIT.
      *****************************************************************
